<i>Oh, no.</i>

255
00:14:09,916 --> 00:14:12,052
‐ [screams]

256
00:14:15,522 --> 00:14:16,456
‐ A sniper!

257
00:14:16,523 --> 00:14:17,624
[clang]

258
00:14:19,593 --> 00:14:20,961
‐ No way!

259
00:14:21,928 --> 00:14:23,363
